---
title: Garlic & Oregano Haloumi Tacos with Lemon Pesto-Dressing & Caramelised Onion
description: The ultimate in one-handed food, these tacos with delicious herbed haloumi, lemon pesto dressing and sweet-sticky caramelised onion are best enjoyed sans cutlery.
